  <listingDescription><![CDATA[<p>Hotel Milano has a lakefront position in the quiet town of Maderno. Step out the doors and you're practically on the promendade, which is perfect for an afternoon stroll. The ferry point is close by for when you want to explore and the hotel's pool is perfect for the days when you want to relax.</p>]]></listingDescription>
