  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Standard Rooms</strong> are 15m² and can sleep up to two people. They have air conditioning, TV, safe, fridge, hairdryer and a shower.</p>
<p><strong>Classic Rooms</strong> are 18m² and can sleep up to two people. They have a balcony with lovely lake views.</p>
<p><strong>Superior Rooms</strong> can sleep up to three people and offer plenty of space at 22m². They have been finished in either a contemporary or Liberty style and have lake views from the balcony. The third bed is a single sofa bed. </p>]]></roomsDescription>
